1
00:00:06,460 --> 00:00:09,460
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

2
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:12,600
Second bow to His Majesty.

3
00:00:14,260 --> 00:00:17,260
Husband and wife bow to each other.

4
00:00:18,360 --> 00:00:19,560
To be of one mind

5
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:21,430
and share weal and woe for life.

6
00:00:24,230 --> 00:00:25,360
Stop!

7
00:00:25,830 --> 00:00:27,360
You cannot get married.

8
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:31,200
Grand Tutor Wei, I have shown enough courtesy.

9
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,729
If you insist on finding fault,

10
00:00:32,729 --> 00:00:34,160
in front of His Majesty today,

11
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,820
don't blame me for being rude.

12
00:00:38,930 --> 00:00:40,360
Your Majesty,

13
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:42,460
General Weibei is going too far.

14
00:00:43,430 --> 00:00:44,500
Your Majesty,

15
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:46,800
I want to expose Shen Luyi's true colors.

16
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,460
What true colors?

17
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:52,530
Your Majesty praised Shen Luyi as a lady of a noble family,

18
00:00:53,060 --> 00:00:55,960
but you don't know that when she was in her boudoir,

19
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:59,220
she had an affair with a stable boy in the Minister's Manor.

20
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,100
I once told General Weibei about this,

21
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:04,430
but he was bewitched by her

22
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:07,660
and didn't mind marrying such a slutty woman.

23
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:09,360
But as the daughter of the Grand Tutor,

24
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:12,460
I disdain to share a husband with a woman of such corrupt morals.

25
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,520
I beg Your Majesty to uphold justice.

26
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:17,530
In front of so many people,

27
00:01:17,530 --> 00:01:19,760
if Lu Jingxing still wants to protect Shen Luyi,

28
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:24,000
this green hat will accompany him for the rest of his life.

29
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,400
I don't believe that a dignified General Weibei

30
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:29,260
could go this far for a woman.

31
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:31,960
I really don't mind,

32
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,100
because

33
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:34,330
I am that stable boy.

34
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,300
The Eldest Miss of the Minister's Manor cherished my talent,

35
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,430
freed me from my slave status,

36
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:41,800
and asked me to practice martial arts and learn to read,

37
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,600
which gave me my current future.

38
00:01:43,930 --> 00:01:44,930
This is impossible.

39
00:01:44,930 --> 00:01:46,900
How could you be that lowly stable boy?

40
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,560
A winged steed is common,

41
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,729
but a Bole is rare.

42
00:01:49,729 --> 00:01:52,060
In my life, I was recognized by the Eldest Miss's discerning eyes

43
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,400
and appreciated by His Majesty.

44
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,759
From a lowly stable boy to General Weibei,

45
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,600
as long as you are loyal to the Emperor and serve the country,

46
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,430
you can all have a bright future.

47
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:04,130
Loyal to the Emperor and serving the country.

48
00:02:04,130 --> 00:02:06,800
When General Weibei joined the battlefield in the northwest,

49
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,930
he reported his background to me.

50
00:02:08,930 --> 00:02:11,060
He never hid it from me.

51
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:13,930
Minister Shen plotted a rebellion

52
00:02:13,930 --> 00:02:15,360
and secretly kept the late Emperor's edict.

53
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,430
Since Lu Jingxing is a stable boy of the Minister's Manor,

54
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,660
he is an accomplice.

55
00:02:19,329 --> 00:02:21,829
Lu Jingxing was beaten half to death by the Minister's Manor

56
00:02:21,829 --> 00:02:23,500
and thrown into a mass grave.

57
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:25,660
If they have a relationship,

58
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:27,100
they are enemies.

59
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:30,560
Then why does he love and respect Shen Zhengran's daughter so much?

60
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:33,600
The daughter of your Grand Tutor's Manor is superficial and unbearable.

61
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,900
Shen Luyi has a noble character and is refined and free from vulgarity.

62
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:39,329
It is natural for General Weibei to love and respect her.

63
00:02:39,329 --> 00:02:41,590
Thank you for your praise, Your Majesty.

64
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,030
Your Majesty.

65
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,760
Lu Jingxing values friendship and righteousness,

66
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,960
a true model.

67
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,630
In order to prevent his sweetheart from suffering humiliation again,

68
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:54,000
I will grant Shen Luyi a first-rank mandate today.

69
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:01,800
Thank you for your reward, Your Majesty.

70
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,900
I thank Your Majesty for your great kindness.

71
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,630
Your Majesty's gift is too precious.

72
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,830
I dare not accept it.

73
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,930
I humbly beg Your Majesty to grant me something else.

74
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:10,130
What do you want?

75
00:03:10,130 --> 00:03:11,330
I beg Your Majesty for mercy

76
00:03:11,330 --> 00:03:13,760
to let me see my father in the death row.

77
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,300
First, to inform him of my marriage.

78
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:17,130
Second, I also want to offer a toast to my father

79
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:19,060
to show a daughter's filial piety.

80
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,660
Granted.

81
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:26,360
I respect Minister Shen for his unyielding character,

82
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,500
and I don't want to kill him.

83
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:29,829
Otherwise, I wouldn't have imprisoned him for so long.

84
00:03:29,829 --> 00:03:32,230
I hope you can persuade your father.

85
00:03:32,230 --> 00:03:34,760
A wise man submits to circumstances.

86
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,700
Yes.

87
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:44,300
Lord Shen, someone is here to see you.

88
00:03:55,230 --> 00:03:56,829
Father, you've suffered.

89
00:03:57,200 --> 00:04:00,060
I suffered a bit when I first came in,

90
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:01,600
but it's been better lately.

91
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,730
I have a doctor and medicine,

92
00:04:02,730 --> 00:04:04,360
hot soup and food for every meal,

93
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,230
and someone even brought me books to read.

94
00:04:06,230 --> 00:04:07,730
I asked around.

95
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:09,360
Lu Jingxing became the General of Weibei,

96
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:12,420
and he secretly asked someone to arrange things for me.

97
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,459
We've found out the truth about the posthumous edict.

98
00:04:17,459 --> 00:04:20,100
Grand Tutor Wei did steal the edict during the house raid.

99
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:21,459
Right now, the edict

100
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:23,130
is hidden in the storehouse of the Grand Tutor's mansion.

101
00:04:23,130 --> 00:04:24,800
I will find a way to get it back

102
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,860
and make it public.

103
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:27,860
Lvyi, you can't.

104
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:31,200
The late Emperor entrusted the edict to me before he died,

105
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,730
and asked me to find his illegitimate son among the people.

106
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:35,230
That child is only six years old.

107
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:36,930
Even if you find the edict

108
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:39,130
and make that child public,

109
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,659
the current Emperor is young and strong.

110
00:04:42,659 --> 00:04:44,520
How could he willingly abdicate?

111
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:47,360
When the time comes, not only will the entire Shen family be executed,

112
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,700
but Lu Jingxing will also be implicated.

113
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:51,860
I am only Jingxing's concubine,

114
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,920
and he knows nothing about the edict.

115
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:55,900
His Majesty has always valued him,

116
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,760
so he will definitely be able to retreat unscathed.

117
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,730
I have been loyal to the late Emperor all my life,

118
00:05:02,730 --> 00:05:04,630
but I ended up like this,

119
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:08,230
and caused our whole family to suffer such hardships.

120
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:12,360
It's all my fault for implicating you.

121
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,100
Although I am a woman,

122
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:15,400
I am also of the Shen family's blood.

123
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,800
I understand your integrity, Father.

124
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,960
I have the Shen family's demeanor and pride.

125
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,290
I am not afraid of death,

126
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:22,460
and neither are Mother and my younger siblings.

127
00:05:22,460 --> 00:05:24,000
My Lvyi has grown up.

128
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:25,830
Today is your wedding day,

129
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,200
but I am in prison,

130
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,900
unable to walk you down the aisle.

131
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,200
Not being able to add to your dowry and congratulate you

132
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,500
is my lifelong regret.

133
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,100
I don't want any regrets.

134
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:38,200
I only pray for your safety, Father.

135
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,530
When I clear our name,

136
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:41,400
I will personally bring you home.

137
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,659
Go.

138
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,900
Live a good life.

139
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:46,030
Protect yourself,

140
00:05:46,030 --> 00:05:47,400
protect Jingxing,

141
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,159
and protect our family.

142
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,760
I will be here,

143
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:52,000
waiting for your return.
